    <thetext>When looking at this bug also consider the errors/warnings placed on @since tags.  Currently api tooling assumes the @since refers to the bundle-version.  When adding support for package versions the @since tags should refer to the package version specified in the bundle manifest Export-Package statement.</thetext>
